cu.explanation_en: GNB_IPV4_ADDRESS_FOR_NGU changed from '192.168.70.133' to '10.0.0.1', which is in a different subnet and unreachable, causing NG-U interface routing failures and preventing proper user plane communication.
cu.explanation_zh: GNB_IPV4_ADDRESS_FOR_NGU 从 '192.168.70.133' 更改为 '10.0.0.1'，该地址位于不同子网且不可达，导致 NG-U 接口路由失败，阻止正确的用户平面通信。

du.explanation_en: T1a_cp_dl changed from [285, 429] to [0, 429], where 0 is below the valid timing range, causing front-haul timing misalignment and synchronization failures.
du.explanation_zh: T1a_cp_dl 从 [285, 429] 更改为 [0, 429]，其中 0 低于有效定时范围，导致前传定时错位和同步失败。
